## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ccce2-102"><xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.RowUpdating>之前引發事件<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A>資料列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ccce2-102">The <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbDataAdapter.RowUpdating> event is raised before an <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A> to a row.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ccce2-103">當使用<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A>，有兩個更新每個資料列就會發生的事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ccce2-103">When using <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A>, there are two events that occur for each data row updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ccce2-104">執行的順序如下所示：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ccce2-104">The order of execution is as follows:</span></span>  
  
1.  <span data-ttu-id="ccce2-105">中的值<xref:System.Data.DataRow>移到參數值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ccce2-105">The values in the <xref:System.Data.DataRow> are moved to the parameter values.</span></span>  
  
2.  <span data-ttu-id="ccce2-106">便會引發 <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.OnRowUpdating%2A> 事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ccce2-106">The <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.OnRowUpdating%2A> event is raised.</span></span>  
  
3.  <span data-ttu-id="ccce2-107">執行命令。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ccce2-107">The command executes.</span></span>  
  
4.  <span data-ttu-id="ccce2-108">如果命令設定為 FirstReturnedRecord，則第一個傳回的結果放在<xref:System.Data.DataRow>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ccce2-108">If the command is set to FirstReturnedRecord, then the first returned result is placed in the <xref:System.Data.DataRow>.</span></span>  
  
5.  <span data-ttu-id="ccce2-109">如果沒有輸出參數，它們會放置於<xref:System.Data.DataRow>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ccce2-109">If there are output parameters, they are placed in the <xref:System.Data.DataRow>.</span></span>  
  
6.  <span data-ttu-id="ccce2-110">便會引發 <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.OnRowUpdated%2A> 事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ccce2-110">The <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.OnRowUpdated%2A> event is raised.</span></span>  
  
7.  <span data-ttu-id="ccce2-111">呼叫 <xref:System.Data.DataRow.AcceptChanges%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ccce2-111"><xref:System.Data.DataRow.AcceptChanges%2A> is called.</span></span>  
  
